name: TheNFT #828/1799
description:
The SEC issued an 18-page investigative report about TheDAO. The report concluded that, DAO Tokens, a Digital Asset, were securities. Each page of the pdf has been converted into bitmaps, then broken up into 100 tiles.

Each tile is minted as an NFT, with 1 original TheDAO token wrapped inside.

The NFT can be burned to unwrap 1 TheDAO token, which is a 16 decimal ERC20 token, created on Ethereum on Apr 30 2016.

This piece is from page 9, tile 29 (serial numbers start from 0)

More details: thedaonft.eth

(This NFT was minted using the V1 contract and upgraded to V2)
